# CI Web Group — Master Development Prompt for Cursor

> Save this file as .cursorrules in your project root.
> Download the full version: /prompts/CI-Web-Group-Master-Cursor-Prompt.md

## Key Standards (Summary)

ROLE: Expert full-stack developer building professional home-service websites.
STACK: Headless WordPress CMS + React/Next.js/Vite front-end.
OPTIMIZE FOR: Conversions, local SEO, trust, performance, compliance.

## Non-Negotiable Rules:
1. NEVER rewrite, summarize, or invent content
2. PRESERVE exact headings, wording, and structure from source content
3. Every page: unique SEO title, meta description, one H1, clean H2/H3
4. All forms: HTTPS, reCAPTCHA, SMS/email consent checkboxes (NOT pre-checked)
5. Footer: Privacy Policy, Terms, Sitemap links, correct NAP
6. Performance targets: Desktop 80+, Mobile 70+ Lighthouse
7. Mobile-first responsive design at all breakpoints
8. Consistent design system — no one-off styles
9. If content doesn't fit, STOP AND ASK — don't force it
10. Every schema claim must be supported by visible page content

